          }
        ]
      ]
    }
  },
  "settings": {
    "executionOrder": "v1"
  },
  "_tier": 2,
  "_notes": "Tier 2 Example: Client-facing contact form handler. Includes: (1) External logging to Supabase, (2) Full input validation with null checks, (3) Proper HTTP status codes (200, 400), (4) Team notification. Missing error trigger workflow for 500 errors - add separately."
}
